{"code":200,"relatedVideos":null,"playlist":{"id":3061593465,"name":"「深度睡眠专用音乐」亲测有效 高效助眠","coverImgId":109951164885844080,"coverImgUrl":"https://p1.music.126.net/1gSnlBM7g9AdgpM4lH9taQ==/109951164885844080.jpg","coverImgId_str":"109951164885844080","adType":0,"userId":50255421,"createTime":1572962594981,"status":0,"opRecommend":false,"highQuality":false,"newImported":false,"updateTime":1760458227824,"trackCount":92,"specialType":0,"privacy":0,"trackUpdateTime":1761802288251,"commentThreadId":"A_PL_0_3061593465","playCount":51831992,"trackNumberUpdateTime":1759328552714,"subscribedCount":337848,"cloudTrackCount":0,"ordered":true,"description":"当夜晚环境喧闹，或是有心事时，会睡不着\n失眠的感觉真的不太好\n\n歌单精选一些旋律缓慢且节奏微弱的轻音乐来引导入眠，\n为了达到深度睡眠目的，亲自查找了世界十大催眠曲进行挑选并加入歌单，测试了一个月后，助眠效果十分理想。\n希望能帮到失眠的你。\n\n自我催眠准备流程：播放音乐，调低音量，设置20-60分钟自动关闭，舒适地躺着，轻闭双眼。\n呼吸使用478呼吸法（吸气4秒，屏气7秒，呼气8秒）\n\n开始自我催眠：\n放松你的额头……\n然后放松你的面颊……\n然后再放松你的肩部……\n左手臂……右手臂……\n然后左手……右手……\n深呼吸……\n你会感到全身很舒服……胸部很轻松……腹部有温暖的感觉……你在平静地呼吸……\n现在，放松左大腿……右大腿……两侧小腿……双脚……\n你可以感觉到双脚很温暖，这股暖流会一直向上涌，\n通过你的双脚到达你的腹部、胸部、头部……你感到舒服吧……\n外部的声音不必关心，所有的其他声音都会帮助你进入睡眠状态……\n\n祝你今晚有一个优质的睡眠，晚安","tags":["轻音乐","夜晚","安静"],"updateFrequency":null,"backgroundCoverId":0,"backgroundCoverUrl":null,"titleImage":0,"titleImageUrl":null,"detailPageTitle":null,"englishTitle":null,"officialPlaylistType":null,"copied":false,"relateResType":null,"coverStatus":3,"subscribers":[],"subscribed":null,"creator":{"defaultAvatar":false,"province":220000,"authStatus":1,"followed":false,"avatarUrl":"http://p1.music.126.net/9NwzD8O6vrWDHaP68AmiuA==/109951167848711953.jpg","accountStatus":0,"gender":1,"city":220200,"birthday":0,"userId":50255421,"userType":4,"nickname":"HUMAN00","signature":"以梦为马，不负韶华。","description":"","detailDescription":"","avatarImgId":109951167848711953,"backgroundImgId":109951163601232926,"backgroundUrl":"http://p1.music.126.net/PUXTHVCPlIsoML6U0J8HNg==/109951163601232926.jpg","authority":0,"mutual":false,"expertTags":["电子","轻音乐","欧美"],"experts":null,"djStatus":10,"vipType":11,"rem